lead_paragraph: Formula One's governing body approved on Friday a new elimination-style qualifying format that will be implemented from this month's Australian season-opener, despite some drivers questioning why it was necessary.

headline.print_headline: FIA Approves New F1 Qualifying Format
headline.main: FIA Approves New F1 Qualifying Format
